### Interruptibility:
- All builtins must respond correctly to `Ctrl+C` (SIGINT) in `interactive mode`.
- `env` or `exit` (when forking) must restore default signal handlers in the child process.

 ğŸ”Œ Connect Signals with Builtin Execution
